{
  "stem": "24409.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They should wear shorts, shorts, because young people of this age usually wear short pants.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Though they wore pants which they had cut off, here and here, and you could see that there was something wrong with it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Though we discussed it with the police, that we are trying to get Jews who are otherwise a burden to Vienna, because they are here without means, but we are trying to get them out.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they fully cooperated with us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had cooperated with the police before this already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was quite active [INAUDIBLE] to tell the police that we organized a boycott of German goods.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The police knew about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we achieved, for example, from the Ministry of Transportation, the trains which usually went to Paris and London via-- via Germany, because it's the shortest way.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But some of these trains were diverted and went via Switzerland, avoiding Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had contact with the police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Which, there was a man called Ulbricht there whose name I remember-- U-L-B-R-I-C-H-T.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there was a Jewish high officer, Gans, G-A-N-S.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "High police officer, from whom we got cooperation with getting the Jews who are unwanted, out of Austria.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But many-- at the end, most of the people came from the [INAUDIBLE], from Czechoslovakia, where the need-- in Poland, where the need was not so urgent as it was in the most eastern part of Czechoslovakia, in Podkarpacka Rus.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Mukachevo was the capital of this part of Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We collected the people in Kottingbrunn, as they came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Betar in Vienna knew of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And very few of them still availed themselves of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were only Betar in from Vienna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I traveled to, I gave speeches in Slovakia, Northern Podkarpacka Rus.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't go that far east anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
